repository_description = "[MVP] Multi-layer Terraform IaC for on-premise GitLab deployment on KVM/QEMU. HA: Kubeadm control plane, Patroni/Postgres, Redis Sentinel, MinIO (erasure coding), Gitaly/Praefect, Vault (hierarchical PKI and AppRole), Harbor Registry, and GitLab Runner. Standalone: Harbor Bootstrapper and Keycloak OIDC SSO. Via Packer, Terraform, and Ansible."
